commit_message:
XIO: refactor _send_cmd to reduce the redundant

Refactor _send_cmd to reduce the redundant and make the code clear:
 * reduce the if statement;
 * use "if params:" instead of "if params != {}:";
 * set params=None as default arg.

Change-Id: I2abcf4242501211a589f1ef78dfbbfd68fc23ab2
